<p><a name="Print" id="Print"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_film&amp;action=edit&amp;section=58" title="Edit section: Print">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Print</span></h3>
<ul>
